settings.section_main_title: WIN TICKETS TO THE MELBOURNE INTERNATIONAL COMEDY FESTIVAL
settings.section_content:
As a local Melbourne brand, we are beyond excited to honour the arts, comedy and the city of Melbourne as the official whiskey of the 2022 Melbourne International Comedy Festival.

To celebrate, we are giving away 5 double passes to a Malbourne International Comedy Festival show. Guaranteed to bring you laughter and good time vibes.
settings.section_note: Terms & Conditions: This competition is run by the Gospel Whiskey. Entry is open between 23 March 2022 12:00am AEST and 5 April 2022 11:59pm. During this period, submit an entry form to be eligible to win. There will be 5 winners who will receive 1x double pass to a 2022 Melbourne International Comedy Show (show dates are 7 April or 13 April). Total prize pool valued at $324. The prizes are not transferable, not redeemable for cash, not for re-sale, and will be awarded to the confirmed winners only. The winners will be choosen at random. Entrants must be 18+ years to enter and living in Aurtalia, excluding NT
